Meet John...

Meet John, a 27 year old journalist. Ever since he, as a young teen, learned about the widespread corruption in his country, after experiencing it first hand himself, he has been driven to stop it.

Study...

John volunteered early on to help with the school paper, and learned that he had a talent for writing. It was only natural to him that he applied to study journalism in the capital University, and was ecstatic when he got accepted.

Career....

He graduated with flying colors, and easily got a job at a top newspaper in his country. John was destined for a great career, but John wanted more.

More...

His disease regarding corruption has never really faded since his teens, but his country had only a resemblance for a free press, and writing about corruption was at best frowned upon. Still he felt repelled to speak up.

The Source...

John was suddenly contacted by an anonymous source, that had heard via a common friend that John might be able to help disclose a scandal involving highly powerful men and their corruption. John agreed to meet.

Secrets...

A secret location was agreed upon, and they met. John was both shocked and repulsed by the scandal his source revealed, but knew he had to get a story publish---

The End

....here the story ends.

 

Shortly after the meeting John mysteriously went missing.

 

John's story was never published.
